root: ^Pfoo, I thought I was going to become part of that wall. I was stuck for a really long time.
^Didn't it cross your mind that you might be to big to wiggle through there by yourself?
^Yes, but I tried holding my breath.
^Is there a possibility I could come with you?
^Please, I really need to go to space!
^It's just that this is kind of MY journey...
^This temple is really old. There are probably a lot of rocks and stuff blocking the way up there. I am strong!
^Okay, you can come along. Let's hope this was the last surprise.
^I will be good! Let's go! Lead the way!
